    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 987.2 generation Cayman S features the desirable 3.4L flat-six with Direct Fuel Injection (DFI), eliminating the IMS bearing concerns of its predecessor. The mid-engine architecture provides an exceptional polar moment of inertia, paired with a crisp 6-speed manual transaxle. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from recent bushing inspections and a precise alignment to factory specifications. It retains the hydraulic steering rack for superior tactile feedback. Braking is handled by four-piston monobloc calipers over vented, cross-drilled rotors, showing minimal swept-area wear. Well-maintained and mechanically sound, this is a driver-focused example ready for the apex.",
